Resume document class
---------------------

resume.cls a simple class file for resumes. 

General usage:

> \documentclass{resume}

> \author{}
> \website{}
> \email{}
> \address{}

> \begin{document}
> \resumeheader

> \section{Objective}
>   Text here.

> \section{Education}

> \begin{itemize}
>     \credential
>       {School} {Location}
>       {Degree} {Duration}
>       {Achievements, etc.}
> \end{itemize}

> ...

Check out resume.tex for an example of usage.

